Hide secrets:
  1) Create a "Map" page
  2) List the invited users (including yourself)
  3) Optionnal: list "Secret" pages
  Send the invitation code (the name of the map)
  Use "hard to guess" names for "Map" pages and "Secret" pages

Send a message to someone:
  Write the message on his/her page

Send a private message to someone:
  1) Create a "UserXxxxx" page
  2) Add the recipient's name on the first line
  3) Tell the recipient about the message

Backup all my pages:
  1) Add "DoHtmlPages" in one of your pages
  2) Click on it
  3) Use your browser to save the html page

Ask for help: Ask a mentor. See LocalMentor.

